examples.en: The department telltale told the boss that his coworkers were taking extra long breaks.
The lodgment of a week's worth of newspapers in the doorway was a telltale sign that the family was away.
He had accidentally disarrayed his brother's CDs, leaving a telltale sign of borrowing without permission.
The media's professional telltales have basically decided that today's celebrities have no right to privacy.
